	Voice of Marriott











Executive Chairman Bill Marriott and Global Culture Officer Debbie Marriott Harrison visit with our longtime partner DC Central Kitchen.









Serve Our World is one of Marriott’s core values and guides how we do business, support our local communities and work to protect the environment. We will continue to share our progress and look forward to launching our latest generation of environmental and social sustainability goals in the near future.









Responsible Business
Our dedication to integrity
and ethical behavior




Environment
Our commitment to protecting
our planet’s natural resources




Our Communities
Our passion to “SERVE Our World”
 










